data.description: Seller is Motivated! Seller is willing to replace the Roof prior to closing or a credit for the roof. This home is not a fixer upper its move in ready.  A charming home in a great location offering 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. There's plenty of space for all the family too, a formal living area and dining space. The kitchen will fit a table and chairs and there is also a laundry room and screen rear porch to enjoy your garden and pool deck. Yes, a private pool and still plenty of yard space! The house itself is in great condition having had all updated plumbing installed and the roof needs to be replaced however, the seller is willing to give a credit or replace prior to closing. Brand new driveway August 2019. The property has easy access to shopping, medical services, restaurants, Full Sail University, Valencia Community College, UCF, and Rollins College. So be quick as this one will not hang around long! Make your offer
